M|Gate|tx|\| Category \| Requirements \|
M|Gate|tx|\|----------\|--------------\|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Completeness** \| All TRD cp have specific technology choices; all dependencies explicit \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Versioning** \| Exact versions specified; no `@latest`; lock files referenced \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Standards Compliance** \| Choices validated against Ring Standards; prohibited packages avoided \|
